00054 void dump(lockid_t &l)
00055 {
00056     cout << "Lock: lspace " << l.lspace() << endl;
00057     cout << "\t vid()=" << l.vid() << endl;
00058 
00059     stid_t stor;

00062 
00063 
00064     lpid_t page;

00071
